text: Horsch is a German last name. It may refer to: * John Horsch (1867-1941), Mennonite historian and writer, father of Elizabeth. * Elizabeth Horsch Bender (1895-1988), American Mennonite editor and translator, daughter of John. == See also == * R. C. Hörsch (born 1943), American photographer, filmmaker, writer, sculptor and musician.
title: Horsch
